lead_paragraph: India will be without three of their first-choice batsmen in the first two tests against England after openers Shikhar Dhawan and KL Rahul, and middle-order batsman Rohit Sharma were ruled out due to injuries.

headline.print_headline: India's Rohit Out of England Tests, Ishant Back
